author: rooneg
msg: Merge r18451 into the merge branch.  The primary change relative to the
version of this code that's in trunk is that we don't have ra_reparent in
1.3.x so we have to close the ra connection and reopen it.
(repos_to_repos_copy): Open our connection in a subpool, and if we
end up trying to copy into a prefix of a path and we're not copying
into the root close the connection by clearing the pool and reopen
